    <h1>🍽️ About EatWhere</h1>
    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>EatWhere</strong> — our office lunch spot finder!
    </p>

    <p>
      After months (or even years!) of eating out near the office, we noticed a recurring problem:
    </p>

    <blockquote>
      “Where to eat ah?”<br />
      “Same old places again?”<br />
