    </blockquote>

    <p>
      We get it. Lunch should be something to look forward to — not a midday headache.
    </p>

    <h2>🥢 What is EatWhere?</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>EatWhere</strong> is a light, fun, and practical web app to help you discover 
      <strong>good food around your workplace</strong>, especially when you're out of ideas or have teammates with different dietary needs.
      <br />
    </p>

    <h2>🍛 What You Can Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>🔍 Filter by cuisine, dietary options, price, and distance</li>
      <li>📍 Browse curated listings of nearby food spots</li>
      <li>🎲 Get “Go Lucky” suggestions for something random</li>
      <li>💬 Read and write reviews to help others</li>
      <li>➕ Submit new food places for the team</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>💬 Why I Built This</h2>
    <p>
      Because food matters and team bonding over meals matters.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you’re looking for something affordable, accommodating dietary needs, or just trying not to eat at the same old kopitiam again — EatWhere is here to help you <strong>eat better, together</strong>.
    </p>

